window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Continuing Stieg Larsson's Millennium Series.</b> </p> <p>In this adrenaline-charged, up-to-the-moment political thriller, Stieg Larsson's Lisbeth Salander and Mikael Blomkvist are back. The troubled genius hacker and crusading journalist thrilled the world in <i>The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo</i>, <i>The Girl Who Played with Fire</i>, and <i>The Girl Who Kicked the Hornet's Nest</i>, which have sold more than 80 million copies worldwide. </p> <p>David Lagercrantz is a Swedish journalist and best-selling author of fiction and nonfiction. He was hand selected by the Larsson estate to write this standalone sequel based on Stieg Larsson's characters. </p>"; 
